# Demo 3D Models

This directory contains placeholder stubs for demo 3D models (.glb format).
In production, these would be Low-Poly cubes or Drei-Drei examples.

Expected files (6 total):
- resonance-7.glb
- ink-protocol.glb
- circuit-garden.glb
- frequency-memory.glb
- sub-bass-cathedral.glb
- velvet-decay.glb

Note: 447-am.jpg and ghost-machine.jpg are 2D-only artworks without 3D models.
